Program: Outlook
Title: Tsunami in Indonesia
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsd5
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The story of the Saudi Arabian family torn apart by the tsunami in Indonesia. Also, the final extracts from the cancer diary of Nick Clarke. Daniel Tammet talks about living with Savant syndrome. Domestic abuse among indigenous communities in Australia. Finally, what its like to be a postman on one of the world's highest border crossings, separating India and China. Show less